These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-1::.
Beverage: 7up, coffee, lemonade, water
Birthday: may, march, july, june
1. Birthday:june is on the left of Beverage:lemonade##1
2. Beverage:7up is on the left of Birthday:march##1
3. Beverage:water is in an odd position##4
4. Birthday:july is on the left or right of Birthday:june##3
5. Beverage:7up is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| Beverage   | 7up | coffee | water | lemonade |
| Birthday        | may | march   | june | july    |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-2::.
Movie-Genre: crime, musical, scientific, superhero
City: edinburgh, new-york, hannover, colone
1. Movie-Genre:musical is on the left of Movie-Genre:superhero##1
2. City:edinburgh is on the left of City:hannover##1
3. City:hannover is in an odd position##4
4. City:edinburgh == Movie-Genre:crime##1
5. City:new-york is on the right of City:hannover##1
6. City:edinburgh == Movie-Genre:crime##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific | crime  | musical  | superhero |
| City   | colone    | edinburgh | hannover | new-york    |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-3::.
Beverage: milk, sprite, lemonade, almond-milk
Movie-Genre: animation, documentary, spy, western
1. Beverage:almond-milk is on the left or right of Movie-Genre:western##3
2. Beverage:lemonade is in an even position##4
3. Movie-Genre:western is on the left or right of Beverage:sprite##3
4. Movie-Genre:western is on the right of Movie-Genre:spy##1
5. Movie-Genre:animation is in an odd position##4
6. Beverage:sprite is on the right of Beverage:lemonade##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4      |
| Beverage          | almond-milk | lemonade | sprite    | milk      |
| Movie-Genre   | spy        | western     | animation | documentary |

