.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-4::.
Hobby: cooking, drawing, reading, woodworking
Beverage: milk, cola, tea, hot-chocolate
1. Hobby:drawing is between Beverage:milk and Beverage:hot-chocolate##2
2. Hobby:woodworking is on the left of Hobby:cooking##1
3. Beverage:tea is in an odd position##4
4. Beverage:cola is on the left of Beverage:hot-chocolate##1
5. Beverage:cola is on the right of Hobby:cooking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Hobby         | woodworking | cooking | drawing | reading |
| Beverage   | tea       | milk   | cola    | hot-chocolate  |

