.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-5::.
Music-Genre: folk, hip-hop, jazz, punk
Sport: swimming, handball, skateboarding, volleyball
1. Music-Genre:jazz is on the right of Sport:volleyball##1
2. Sport:handball == Music-Genre:punk##1
3. Sport:skateboarding is on the right of Music-Genre:folk##1
4. Music-Genre:hip-hop is on the far left##1
5. Music-Genre:jazz is in an odd position##4
6. Sport:swimming is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |     4      |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop  | folk    | jazz   | punk       |
| Sport   | swimming | volleyball | skateboarding | handball |

