.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-10::.
Beverage: almond-milk, cola, juice, soy-milk
Flower: daffodil, amaryllis, lily, tulip
1. Beverage:almond-milk == Flower:tulip##1
2. Flower:daffodil is on the right of Beverage:almond-milk##1
3. Flower:tulip is between Flower:daffodil and Beverage:juice##2
4. Beverage:almond-milk is in an odd position##4
5. Flower:tulip is on the left or right of Flower:daffodil##3
6. Beverage:cola is on the left or right of Flower:amaryllis##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3      |    4     |
| Beverage      | cola       | juice   | almond-milk | soy-milk |
| Flower   | lily | amaryllis | tulip        | daffodil    |

