.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-18::.
Beverage: 7up, fanta, milk, water
City: edinburgh, san-francisco, paris, miami
1. City:san-francisco is on the far left##1
2. Beverage:milk is on the left or right of Beverage:7up##3
3. Beverage:water is on the far left or far right##3
4. City:paris is on the left of City:miami##1
5. City:miami is on the right of Beverage:7up##1
6. City:paris is in an even position##4
7. City:edinburgh == Beverage:fanta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |   2    |     3      |   4   |
| Beverage   | water | 7up    | milk       | fanta |
| City       | san-francisco  | paris | miami | edinburgh  |

